com.adobe.cq.social.moderation.dashboard.api

Interface FilterGroup

  • All Superinterfaces:
    SocialComponent

    @ProviderType
public interface FilterGroup
extends SocialComponent
    A FilterGroup actually contains several groups of filters for searching in the moderation dashboard. Each group within is treated as a logical AND with the other groups, but within each group the selected filters are ORed together for the search.
